snippet.textDisplay: This actually makes sense.  My 83 year old mother in law got COVID 19 and had not symptoms.  She takes Vitamin D every day.  We were sure that if she got the virus she was going to end up in the hospital.  Out of 7 people in the house only two had no symptoms.  Her and my 9 year old grandson.
